WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.400
Every sound can become a trail.

00:03.500 --> 00:07.300
Listen: tap play and hear one chord. [Piano chord]

00:07.400 --> 00:11.000
Choose: tap the color you hear.

00:11.100 --> 00:15.100
Why colors? Ear first, names later. Colors name whole sounds. After nine are strong, note names join in.

00:15.200 --> 00:20.000
Explore the sounds. Tap any color to hear its sound. [Guitar chord]

00:20.100 --> 00:23.300
Grow with tiny sessions, one step at a time.

00:23.400 --> 00:26.000
Listen. Choose. Grow. Pitch Trail.
